  "instructions": [
    "Cook the macaroni according to the package instructions until al dente.",
    "Drain the macaroni and set it aside.",
    "In a large saucepan, combine the rapeseed oil, sour cream, chopped fresh dill, chopped fresh parsley, salt, black pepper, lemon juice, and dried marjoram.",
